    "description": "Neural Group Inc. offers AI and media services. The company provides DigiFlow for creation of smart city solutions for people, goods and security, mobility and moving vehicles, and infrastructure and facilities; and DigiPark, which provides parking lot operators, logistics facilities, real estate developers, commercial facilities, tourist facilities, SA/PA, and public parking lots with safety monitoring and guidance services. It also provides SIGN DIGI that provides AI signage services to commercial facilities, office buildings, and smart cities; RemoDesk, a service that ensures business security in a remote environment; and AI MD, an AI-driven fashion trend analysis service that offers information on fashion trends to analyze data from SNS sites, shopping sites, and other services. In addition, the company provides KizunaNavi, 1-on-1 support service; FOCUS CHANNEL, a signage media platform; NeuralVision, an end-to-end service for AI-powered LED vision displays; and Generative Web to edit web pages. Neural Group Inc. was formerly known as Neural Pocket Inc. and changed its name to Neural Group Inc. in June 2023. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
